{"tid":1710893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一個方法教大家救中大手足","createTime":"2019-11-12T09:07:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T09:13:11.000Z","uid":264440,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"83778369f23b30c1df6226bfe4f816adc0ab5c89","tid":1710893,"uid":264440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:07:08.000Z","msg":"知唔知點解依家連登冇被ddos緊<br />\n就係想連登仔度係度嘈應該去邊唔去邊 猶豫不決而遲遲未行動<br />\n想救中大手足 睇到呢個po既你 無論係<br />\n入中大支援<br />\n入中大附近範圍開花 反包圍<br />\n係自己地區開花<br />\n中大碧秋樓<br />\n狗舍<br />\n中聯辦<br />\n咩都好<br />\n做自己認為可以救到手足 分散狗力既野<br />\n唔好係度嘈邊樣先係正確答案 兄弟爬山正是時候<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人 即刻行動！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"526995d30f570c10c17d1e8db35f4c8318a9c0e1","tid":1710893,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:07:56.000Z","msg":"❗️❗️中大告急，中大告急❗️❗️<br />\n出唔到去嘅人幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=UyoO8KdNfTPb55o7yEEco60EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=6aa80571\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n 然後打 /task 攞任務<br />\n<br />\n今日Task分類<br />\n/task1: 中環罷工<br />\n/task2: 其他中國同香港議題<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">/task3: </span></span>⚠️中大 ⚠️<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Rt + like + reply </span><br />\n<br />\n幫推<br />\n(突發）幫手救中大（twitter戰線）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1710885\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1710885</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6c7ed7765f85287b357a890352d01cb7d3cdc218","tid":1710893,"uid":264440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:08:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1a1d0957b5cc2e8d45c090ff5387d8dca2bcdf3","tid":1710893,"uid":264440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:09:14.000Z","msg":